In the future, please put the overall scale back on the remaining screens after the warm-up. I'm fairly certain that the 'probable' as the center and 'possible' was just below it, but I'm not COMPLETELY certain. This is important because people will estimate in ranges of 20% (there were 5 choices) if they are rational. Or even if they are not, numbers and probabilities still dictate our intuitive responses, contra aesthetic theorists. Good luck with the results!
